    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：</strong> 强烈推荐使用耳机。在合作模式下，麦克风是进行语音聊天的必需品，它会触发幽灵。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一起合作！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个试玩版中，你和朋友被困在两个相连的房子中。你们需要共同解决独特而神秘的谜题以逃脱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/9ed94d453f538a26749b9254506d18fa.avif?t=1761587957\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>避开实体！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩过程中，一个盲眼实体在阴影中游荡，在房子之间来回徘徊，试图抓住你。你必须不惜一切代价避开它！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/194c2604c6cca8b7d9ff3904c2de3acc.poster.avif?t=1761587957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/194c2604c6cca8b7d9ff3904c2de3acc.webm?t=1761587957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/194c2604c6cca8b7d9ff3904c2de3acc.mp4?t=1761587957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>保持安静！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩中的实体可能是盲眼的，但它能听到一切！每当听到它时，你必须非常安静，否则它会来找你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/7d2444a26a8785f8b796f44bf02a37e7.poster.avif?t=1761587957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/7d2444a26a8785f8b796f44bf02a37e7.webm?t=1761587957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/7d2444a26a8785f8b796f44bf02a37e7.mp4?t=1761587957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>救你的朋友！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果实体在试玩中抓住了你的朋友，他们会被关在一个笼子里。你必须迅速行动，在实体抓住你之前将他们解救出来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/fb148dc63f331d890a41b6030717496d.poster.avif?t=1761587957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/fb148dc63f331d890a41b6030717496d.webm?t=1761587957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/fb148dc63f331d890a41b6030717496d.mp4?t=1761587957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一起逃脱！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场试玩冒险中，你和你的朋友能在时间耗尽之前逃脱实体的掌控吗？</p>",
